法規內容.條文內容:
The following items shall be included in the organization rules of a veterinarian association:
1        The name of the association;
2        Purpose;
3        Area;
4        Address;
5        Functions or business;
6        Organization;
7        Membership and cancellation of membership;
8        Obligation of the members;
9        Number, limits of authorities, terms of office of directors or supervisors, as well as their election and dismissal;
10       Meetings;
11       General rules to be followed by members;
12       Standard for remuneration for members performing their duties
13       Fee and accounting;
14       Amendment of organization rules;
15      Other necessary matters to be described in accordance with relevant regulations.
